project_descr:
"Horizons Project – Strengthening Community Resilience in Abkhazia"
Objective: to promote the social and economic resilience of local communities, especially youth, through improved access to high quality health and education services.

outputs.output_descr: 1/ improved access to quality health services for Abkhazia vulnerable population; 2/ Improved access to quality education, skills dev-nt & social participation opportunities for children/youth; 3/ Enhanced dialogue across youth and professional groups.
donor_name: UNITED STATES AGENCY FOR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (USAID)
